cat << EOF
Lsdvd is a C application for reading the contents of a DVD and printing the
contents to your terminal. It provides Name of the disc, number of tracks,
length, format, aspect of each track, Format, language, number of channels,
contents etc... of each audio track, language and contents of each
subtitle..and more.
